      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy the ride. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one\u2014it\u2019s been garage-kept, hand-washed every Sunday, and it still feels like it just rolled off the lot. It\u2019s in truly pristine shape; I think there's one tiny little mark on the lower trim that you'd need a magnifying glass to find, but otherwise, she's perfect. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that looks and drives like a dream, you\u2019ve found it. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
