    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered here is a pristine E92 M3, a true masterpiece of atmospheric engineering. The S65 V8 screams to its 8,400 RPM redline with surgical precision, benefiting from proactive rod bearing replacement using VAC coated shells and ARP bolts to ensure long-term bottom-end integrity. The M-DCT transmission has been flashed with GTS software for lightning-fast shift logic and optimized clamping pressures. Chassis dynamics are razor-sharp thanks to refreshed subframe bushings and EDC-calibrated dampers that provide an uncompromising contact patch. This is a zero-fault, high-spec example with a documented service history that ensures the VANOS system and throttle actuators remain in peak operating parameters. No leaks, no codes, just pure mechanical synergy. Truly a collector-tier specimen for the discerning pilot.",
